    "body": "## Purpose\n\nSome users are worried about logs:\n\n```bash\n(EngineCore_3 pid=704) DEBUG 08-04 12:28:48 [deep_gemm_moe.py:55] DeepGemm disabled: unaligned problem size. M: 32, N: 2048, K: 7168\n(EngineCore_3 pid=704) DEBUG 08-04 12:28:48 [deep_gemm_moe.py:55] DeepGemm disabled: unaligned problem size. M: 112, N: 2048, K: 7168\n```\n\nSo this PR make the log more cleaner and look better.\n\n## Test\n\n```bash\n(EngineCore_3 pid=704) DEBUG 08-04 12:28:48 [deep_gemm_moe.py:55] DeepGemm disabled: unaligned problem size. M: 32, N: 2048, K: 7168\n(EngineCore_3 pid=704) DEBUG 08-04 12:28:48 [deep_gemm_moe.py:55] DeepGemm disabled: unaligned problem size. M: 112, N: 2048, K: 7168\n```\n\nNow:\n\n```bash\n(EngineCore_3 pid=704) DEBUG 08-04 14:36:48 [deep_gemm_moe.py:55] DeepGemm disabled for this problem size. M: 32, N: 2048, K: 7168. This log means we will fallback to triton for this specific shape for further speed up.\n```",
